graph TD
    subgraph Internet[Internet - Untrusted Zone]
        Actor[External User / Browser]
    end

    subgraph DMZ[DMZ - Perimeter Defense]
        WAF[WAF - OWASP CRS Rules v3.3]
        Gateway[API Gateway - Rate Limiting and TLS Termination]
    end

    subgraph Internal[Internal Network - Application Tier]
        Frontend[Frontend - React SPA with CSP Headers]
        API[API Backend - Spring Boot with JWT Validation]
        AuthSvc[Auth Service - BCrypt cost 12 and Session Management]
        MFA[MFA Provider - TOTP RFC 6238]
    end

    subgraph DataZone[Data Zone - Encrypted Storage]
        DB[PostgreSQL - AES-256 Encryption at Rest]
        Vault[Key Vault - HashiCorp Vault Secret Rotation]
    end

    Actor -->|HTTPS TLS 1.3 only - HTTP rejected| WAF
    WAF -->|XSS and SQLi payloads filtered - clean requests only| Gateway
    Gateway -->|Rate limit 5 req per min per IP - 429 on excess| API
    Gateway -->|Static assets HTTPS CDN| Frontend
    API -->|JWT Bearer RS256 signed - algorithm none rejected| AuthSvc
    AuthSvc -->|TOTP code verification - 30s window| MFA
    MFA -->|OTP code via secure channel| Actor
    AuthSvc -->|PreparedStatement queries - no string concatenation| DB
    API -->|Parameterized SQL only - no dynamic concatenation| DB
    DB -->|Encryption key rotation every 90 days| Vault

    style Internet fill:#ffebee,stroke:#ef5350,color:#000
    style DMZ fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#ffc107,color:#000
    style Internal fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50,color:#000
    style DataZone fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3,color:#000
